 * src/sci_cb.c:
   Only remove extra space indent after a multiline comment if the
   indent contains one too many spaces.
 * src/highlighting.c, data/filetypes.d:
   Show D typedefs in bold.
 * src/sci_cb.c, src/sci_cb.h, src/document.c:
